adviseScripts.text: Master,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: what do you think of my outfit?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: It looks good on you.
... But I feel like something's missing.
R-really? Well... It's not like I specifically wore this for you...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: but I suppose I can wear it more often in the future.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I-it's not as if I dressed up in this to please you, so it doesn't matter.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: ... Anyway, what do you think is missing?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I talk about outfits.
Master,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: how many stars would you give my service?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Five stars, obviously.
I dunno... One?
I knew you'd say that!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You know why?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Honestly, if it were you, I figured you'd be content with my service.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Wait, what? Just one?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: W-why would you even say that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I know I may be lacking, but I don't think I'm that bad!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: So, what part of it did you not like? Just be honest with me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I talk about her service.
Master,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: if you had to pick someone to be your exclusive maid,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: would you rather have me or Drake?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Drake.
You.
What?! Why?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Ah, well... Everyone has different tastes, right?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I guess I could, like, call Drake over here or something?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Hehe.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I knew you'd choose me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Though becoming someone's exclusive maid isn't exactly my thing,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I suppose I can make an exception for you, Master.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I talk about what goes into being an exclusive maid.
Ugh... This maid outfit is so uncomfortable.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I can't wait to take it off.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You can always change into something more comfortable here.
Need my help with your dress?
I would if I could.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: But, I didn't bring any change of clothes.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Um... I-if it's okay with you, Master...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: c-can I borrow your shirt for a moment?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: W-w-what did you say?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Oh, Master, I didn't expect that from you!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Wow, you're really full of mischief!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I talk about maid outfits.
Soda wants me to help her with cleaning after we're done today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: ... Is there any way we can extend today's session?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I absolutely hate cleaning.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You're free to hide in the Commander's Room.
Sorry, but our session is over. I'll contact Soda right away.
The Commander's Room? Well, that's not a bad idea.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Where specifically should I hide, though?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: The shower might be the best place...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Wh-what?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: It hasn't even been ten minutes since I got here.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: That's hardly what I'd call a proper counseling session!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You're pulling my leg, aren't you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I spend some time in the Commander's Room with Privaty.
No matter how many times I do it, I can never get used to saying "Master".
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What do you think about being called Master?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: It does feel a bit funny at times, because I'm not used to it.
It feels wonderful when you call me that.
Okay, so I'm not the only one after all.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Wait...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What do you mean you feel funny when I call you Master?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Co-come again? You like it when I call you that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Hehe! In that case, I'll call you that whenever I'm dressed as a maid.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Who knows, maybe I'll get used to it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I talk about forms of address.
Cocoa made me a ketchup cake today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: It's not like anything I've had before, but it wasn't half bad.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You certainly have... unique tastes.
I'm a big fan of ketchup cake as well.
Hey, don't judge me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Once you get used to it, it tastes kinda similar to this dessert they serve at one of those Royal Road cafes.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: It's nice to see we've got the same tastes.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Just thinking about it is enough to make my mouth water...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Fo-forget that last bit I said!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I talk about the ketchup cake.
M-Master,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: are you back?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I'm back, my little kitty cat.
Ki-ki-kitty cat?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Ar-are you saying I'm as adorable as a kitty?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: ... Why are you not saying anything?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Oh, come on! A little witty comeback wouldn't hurt, you know!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Hmph!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I spend a joyful counseling session with Privaty.
A customer complimented me today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I have to say, it feels good whenever that happens.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: That's because you're totally the best!
*Pats Privaty on the head*
... What do you think you're doing right now?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: H-h-hey, what's this?! You startled me!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: ... Customers usually shower me with compliments,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: but I guess your praise isn't too bad either.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I spend some time giving Privaty more compliments.
I had to run some errands at the Courthouse today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: When I got back, Yulha and Admi were just staring at me, not saying a word.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Why do you think they were doing that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Because you're so adorable in that outfit.
Because you look a bit strange in that outfit.
Y-you mean Yulha and Admi think I'm cute?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: ... I'll have to ask them the next time I see them.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What about you, Master? Do you find me cute in this?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I-I was just wondering, that's all!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: W-what?! How so?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Hold on... you don't think I look strange in this outfit, do you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I have a nice heart-to-heart.
I wonder if it's because of my job at the Maid Cafe,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: but I've been craving sweets these days.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What's your favorite dessert, Master?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Chocolate that's smeared on your lips.
I like pretty much anything that's sweet.
Excuse me?! Did you just say what I think you said?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You really have no filter, do you, Master?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Wow, really? That's unexpected.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I thought you wouldn't be a big fan of sweets.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Well, if you happen to visit the Maid Cafe next time, I'll whip up a sugary treat for you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I talk about snacks.
Ahem.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Ade gave me some cooking tips today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Is there anything special you'd like me to prepare for you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I'm sure I'll like anything you make.
I'm fine as long as it's edible.
W-will you really like whatever I make?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: In that case... I'll make you some omurice that I'm pretty good at.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Just so you know, the only shape I learned to make is a heart,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: so don't go reading too much into it!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What do you mean by that?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Are you saying you don't trust my cooking skills?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I talk about cooking.
I've got to draw on my customers' omurice,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: but I don't know what to draw...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: How about your face?
How about my face?
M-my face?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: ... I've never really thought about it,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: but if that's what you think people would like, I guess I could consider it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Eh? Your face?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I don't really think that'll be in high demand...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: No, I'm sure there might be at least one person who'd be into it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I talk about what other things she can draw.
M-Master...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Why do you keep staring at me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Because you're so pretty.
Because you've got some ketchup on your face.
Y-you find me pretty?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I know you're just flattering me... but it's working.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Wha...? I-I do?! W-where?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You should have told me earlier!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I don't have a mirror right now... Would you mind wiping it off for me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I have an enjoyable session with Privaty.
The dishes are actually done before they're brought out, you know.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Do you really think that reciting spells will somehow enhance the flavor?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: It seems to be getting more delicious, doesn't it?
Privaty, Privaty, on the count of three, you will fall in love with me! 1... 2...
You're actually buying into these absurd spells too?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Fine, I guess we can give it a shot and test some of them out.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: W-wait! You shouldn't be reciting that kind of thing!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Maybe you should... Gah, I just don't know!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I spend time reciting spells with Privaty.
*Sigh*
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What's the big deal about being served by a maid, anyway?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I just don't get it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: What would you like to have, Madam?
I don't quite understand it myself, to be honest.
W-what did you just call me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Okay. I think I'm starting to see the appeal.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: As expected! You think the same way, huh?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Wait...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: does that mean you don't understand my maid service either?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I further discuss the concept of maids.
Mmwaaah!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I wonder if it'd be cuter if I make the heart like this...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: As I enter the Commander's Room, I see Privaty on her own, practicing making hearts with her hands.
M-Master?! Y-you didn't see that just now, did you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Make a heart gesture with your hands to Privaty.
Nope, I didn't see anything.
W-what is that supposed to mean?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You're not... confessing your love to me, are you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Phew...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Thank goodness!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I make heart gestures to each other during our counseling session.
No matter how much I practice, I can't seem to memorize those spells.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I ended up asking a professional voice actor to record it for me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Would you like to listen?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I'd prefer to hear your voice.
The vibe really hits differently since she is a professional voice actor.
Y-you would?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Ahem.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: All right, I'll recite the spell just for you.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I know, right? I mean, she is like the most famous voice actor in Ark.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: ... But you don't like it better than my own voice, do you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I talk about voices.
My meeting ran late, so I hurriedly made my way to the Commander's Room. There, I find Privaty holding a cake.
M-Master! I made this cake for y...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Agh!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Grab Privaty.
Grab the cake.
Oh no!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: The cake's all ruined now...
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Your safety is more important than a cake.
I-it's just a bit embarrassing to hear you say that all of a sudden!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: *Crash*
... Are you okay?
... I'm fine. You and your precious cake can live happily ever after!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I'll leave you two alone. Hmph!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I have a pleasant counseling session with Privaty.
Out of all of us,
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: who do you suppose comes closest to being the perfect maid?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You.
Soda.
Hmm? I certainly didn't expect you to say that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Then again, I suppose I did do a decent job at the Maid Cafe.
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: You've really got a keen eye, don't you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Huh? Soda?
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Just today, she tripped and shattered a whole tray of cups!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: I get that she's been at this maid thing longer and all, but... how could you just!
adviseScripts.speaker: Privaty

adviseScripts.text: Privaty and I discuss the finer points of being a perfect maid.
